en.title: FusionExcel Sponsors Malacca Orang-Utan Hash House Harriers 10th Anniversary Run 14th March 2009!
en.content: FusionExcel is proud to sponsor the Malacca Orang-Utan Hash House Harriers 10th Anniversary Run on 14th March 2009. The run was attended by Well over 1,000 participants attended the run from many parts of the world, including Singapore, Philippines, Indonesia, Thailand, Australia, Switzerland, Netherlands, etc. FusionExcel's dynamic President Director Chow Chong Seng attended the event together with FusionExcel Leader Tony Lim. They conducted demonstrations using FusionExcel's Quantum Pendant with the enthusiastic participants who were all amazed by the power of the Quantum Pendant! There were some participants who bought a set or two on the spot!
